        <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Module Contract\/ \:</para>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  Provide the package entry point for line type classifiers — modules that classify each document line as a header, list item, table of contents entry, raw text, or other structural type. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>\par \b Scope\/ \:  Package initialization for line_type_classifiers subpackage. \par \b Input\/ \:  None (package-level). \par \b Output\/ \:  Public symbols re-exported from classifier modules. \par \b Links\/ \:  [USES_API(8): <ref refid="namespacededoc_1_1structure__extractors_1_1feature__extractors" kindref="compound">dedoc.structure_extractors.feature_extractors</ref>] \par \b Invariants\/ \:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Every document line receives exactly one line type label. \par \b Rationale\/ \:</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
